name: Deleted entry
classes: Glycosidases, i.e. enzymes that hydrolyse O- and S-glycosyl compounds
comment: Deleted entry: ribosylhomocysteinase. This enzyme was transferred to EC 3.13.1.2, 5-deoxyribos-5-ylhomocysteinase, which has since been deleted. The activity is most probably attributable to EC 4.4.1.21, S-ribosylhomocysteine lyase
